lead_paragraph: Cologne fans organised a sit-down protest to block the team bus of opponents RB Leipzig on Sunday, forcing the Bundesliga match to start 15 minutes late.

headline.print_headline: Cologne Fans Delay Leipzig Team Bus With Sit-Down Protest
